title: Von Miller interview, Zeke suspension, season predictions (Football 09/06)
description:
Nick Kostos and Will Brinson discuss the impact of postponing Bucs-Dolphins due to Hurricane Irma (8:08), along with another update on Ezekiel Elliott's suspension (14:21). Then, the guys welcome on Super Bowl L MVP Von Miller (23:57). The Broncos All-Pro LB talks about Denver releasing T.J. Ward (25:37), the team bringing back Brock Osweiler (27:16), and his Aggies' collapse vs. UCLA (30:05). Next, Nick and Pete give their season predictions (34:33), and over/under picks (41:41).
